1.00	Danger_Zone_(Gladiators)	Assault (Gladiators)	Assault (Danger Zone) is an event played in several incarnations of the television series Gladiators. In this event, a contender must navigate their way across a number of safety stations (each housing their own weapon) aiming for a target located above the Gladiator who is standing on a raised podium with a tennis ball gun, their target being the contender.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4c/Dangerzone4.jpg/320px-Dangerzone4.jpg
